titles.title: A bill to provide for the liquidation or reliquidation of certain entries relating to high-density laminate panels entered from 1997 through 2005.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 5/25/2006--Introduced. Directs the Bureau of Customs and Border Protection to provide for the liquidation or reliquidation of certain entries relating to high-density laminate panels.
